Usage: set_ideal_latency [-help] <latency_value> <object_list> [-fall] [-max]
                         [-min] [-rise]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
<latency_value>     # Specifies the ideal latency value (float, required)
<object_list>       # List of objects: instance pins or ports
                    # (string, required)
-fall               # Sets ideal latency with respect to fall edge
                    # (bool, optional)
-max                # Sets ideal latency with respect to max corner
                    # (bool, optional)
-min                # Sets ideal latency with respect to min corner
                    # (bool, optional)
-rise               # Sets ideal latency with respect to rise edge
                    # (bool, optional)